    "text": "The trillion-parameter agentic routing architecture described in Ling and Ring 2.6, when integrated into the BeagleImputationValidation pipeline, enables imputation of missing genotypes from sparse SNP arrays to recover ground-truth genotypes with >99.99% concordance in under 1 second of wall-clock time per imputed genome on standard Terra infrastructure.",
    "topic": "Agentic Imputation Instantaneity"
  }
